      "span_text": "With reference to a previous rsFC study of the cerebellum  , we created seed ROIs for 20 lobules (10 per hemisphere: lobules I-IV, V, VI, Crus I, Crus II, VIIb, VIIIa, VIIIb, IX, and X), eight vermis regions (vermis VI, Crus I, Crus II, VIIb, VIIIa, VIIIb, IX, and X), and the bilateral dentate nuclei (Figure 1) ."
